      "content": "that's helpful. i guess my main issue is that it feels less like a \"tide\" and more like something's just constantly nibbling away at our capacity in the background. it's really hard to track because it's not one big thing, just a bunch of tiny, annoying little bits of work that show up out of nowhere. any tips for catching those little things before they pile up?",
